title: 597. 10 Takeaways from Week 5
itunes:title: 597. 10 Takeaways from Week 5
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and pick ten storylines that stood out from Week 5 of the NFL season. To start off, the guys discuss how the Cowboys moved on to win after the injury of QB Dak Prescott (1:05). Next, the trio examine how great Seahawks QB Russell Wilson is after his clutch performance against the Vikings (3:53). Later, the guys look at how the Raiders put the league on notice after their win at the Chiefs (23:30). To wrap up the show, DJ, Bucky and Rhett discuss if QB Jimmy Garoppolo's era is over in San Francisco (33:32). All that and more in this packed episode.
